English(en): Doesn’t do a lot of deep introspection, but will get the job done reliably.
Was serving french fries at a fast food restaurant last month. Does good work when he applies himself.
Trained at the world’s finest feline universities. Has cat like reflexes, but sometimes takes cat naps.
One of space’s most preeminent rocketry experts as well as a top cosmic sports athlete. Conducts great research when he isn’t distracted by his adoring fans.
His knowledge of legumes is surpassed only by his knowledge of rocket science. Always researches quickly and masterfully.
